{"tid":1442021,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"班狗成日喺住宅區放蛋，唔明點解班街坊唔拉消防喉射佢老味","createTime":"2019-08-10T20:12:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T20:32:00.000Z","uid":288812,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bd10eb64a461f7eaaf21da089f282120c6ebdd72","tid":1442021,"uid":288812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T20:12:21.000Z","msg":"如題，如果班狗喺我屋企樓下放蛋，我實爆消防喉玻璃開喉喺十幾樓射啲蛋同班狗，佢上樓拉我又如何，上到庭咪話屋企有老有嫩，出於保護佢地健康出手囉，我唔信咁都告得我入，如果住低層，放條喉落街俾前線手足都夠長啦。莫非而家啲樓無消防喉？"},{"pid":"971d93be13692160f06f6659a5a2398ebe0b8337","tid":1442021,"uid":71713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T20:20:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a95751412ad93004970490a0f771a8610daee328","tid":1442021,"uid":288812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T20:30:18.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"ec9ead06eadc730124aeb1ba84982b3b06ce9796","tid":1442021,"uid":288812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T20:30:29.000Z","msg":"五"},{"pid":"0c2ce316a3c3db74b4434fc0b1dc3544cef71ab2","tid":1442021,"uid":288812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec9ead06eadc730124aeb1ba84982b3b06ce9796","tid":1442021,"uid":288812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T20:30:29.000Z","msg":"五"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T20:30:52.000Z","msg":"大"},{"pid":"33bb7e9e1d15b95ef18fb6e7607155207047cd67","tid":1442021,"uid":288812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c2ce316a3c3db74b4434fc0b1dc3544cef71ab2","tid":1442021,"uid":288812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec9ead06eadc730124aeb1ba84982b3b06ce9796","tid":1442021,"uid":288812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T20:30:29.000Z","msg":"五"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T20:30:52.000Z","msg":"大"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T20:31:02.000Z","msg":"訴"},{"pid":"290d10dabbfedfec5a0897bfcbd6559f8363ce2a","tid":1442021,"uid":288812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote